    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>In the Napster saga (editorial, July 29), one thing has been painfully obvious: Many people are eager to get something for nothing -- even if it means stealing.</p>
        <p>MATT C. ABBOTT  Chicago, July 29, 2000</p>
